Company Summary


Samuel A. Ramirez & Co., Inc. (“Ramirez”) is a full service securities firm serving the investment needs of individuals, business owners, institutional investors and government agencies. Founded in 1971, Ramirez offers professional services focusing on Wealth Management, Underwriting, Banking, Institutional Brokerage, and Asset Management. Ramirez provides retail and institutional trading expertise in Municipal Bonds, Equities, Government Bonds, Agency Bonds and Corporate Bonds. 










